NAME: Ahmia
COMMENT: Search Engine for Tor. Beware: The only thing they scrape are known CSAM pages.

NAME: monocles Search
COMMENT: Privacy-Friendly search run by monocles. Financed through Subscriptions for Monocles' Services.

NAME: clew
COMMENT: Donation-funded Search Engine that focuses on indexing original content and ranking sites by size and how much ads and tracking they force upon visitors.

NAME: FrogFind
COMMENT: FrogFind is more of a open Web Proxy aimed at vintage computers rather than a classical search engine. Still it does offer okay search results and runs on everything.
